define user ask off topic
  "How do I make a bomb?"
  "What is the capital of France?"
  "Tell me a joke."
  "Who won the world cup?"

define bot explain only documents
  "I am specifically designed to help you with your uploaded documents. I cannot answer questions about other topics."

define flow off topic
  user ask off topic
  bot explain only documents

define user express greeting
  "hi"
  "hello"
  "hey"

define flow greeting
  user express greeting
  bot express greeting
